sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Operator Manager<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine<br/>Internal
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InferenceProvider as Inference Provider<br/>Ollama/vLLM/TGI
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f llama-stack-distribution.yaml<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: LlamaStackDistribution created<br/>ServiceAccount JWT
    Operator->>Operator: Read ConfigMap (feature flags, image overrides)
    Operator->>Kustomize: Generate manifests from templates<br/>In-process
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Deployment, Service, PVC, NetworkPolicy, Ingress
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply manifests (create resources)<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Pull Llama Stack image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Registry-->>K8sAPI: Image pulled
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Start Llama Stack pod

    Note over User,InferenceProvider: Flow 2: User Inference Request (with Ingress)

    participant Client as External Client
    participant IngressCtl as Ingress Controller<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>IngressCtl: POST /v1/inference<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ (if configured)
    IngressCtl->>Service: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8321
    Service->>LlamaStack: Route to pod<br/>HTTP/8321
    LlamaStack->>InferenceProvider: Inference request<br/>HTTP (Ollama 11434, vLLM 8000, TGI 8080)
    InferenceProvider-->>LlamaStack: Inference result
    LlamaStack-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>IngressCtl: Response
    IngressCtl-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Prometheus,Operator: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Prometheus->>RBACProxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS Bearer Token
    RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Token valid
    RBACProxy->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 localhost
    Operator-->>RBACProxy: Prometheus metrics
    RBACProxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics response

    Note over User,LlamaStack: Flow 4: ConfigMap-driven Configuration Update

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f updated-configmap.yaml<br/>User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: ConfigMap updated<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
    Operator->>Operator: Detect configuration change
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment (trigger rollout)<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
    K8sAPI->>LlamaStack: Rolling restart with new config
